age_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_BACKDROP", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974740_1016398220029488_5978086061316473391_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=z5_vtNIPJ18Q7kNvgGJ2n6D&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDxju1_gSyAOmroXd_KqgenTS0qqO_7KGlHcTA6B5fbPg&oe=672A061A"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "859621013029002", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031434_859621016362335_4237294879850559984_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0Wkl_r_5ng4Q7kNvgH4ni5Y&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD1F4UzlGXodnLI7s57tDk3On80QNt0LG4SMaFmIfyiog&oe=6729F9B8"}, {"file_name": "Hero_Cover.png", "id": "542283291765376", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569433_542283295098709_195628269235225195_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=j55LgqOXuhsQ7kNvgElxFpj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCSE6e_HFbsJgHBQS7GF_zIO77Bu9bcfl3PXITnBK9jCw&oe=672A133A"}, {"file_name": "AE_img_Immersive_Object_Right.png", "id": "374090292402577", "image_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_OBJECT_RIGHT", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974582_374090295735910_5616989277460252096_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qn57hqjHnrQQ7kNvgHjw8D2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKLsVRpb-75BAqYSQKFTA9ja_CvZcjKf3F6IwZokeBsg&oe=672A216D"}]}, "id": "925661796152132", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "screenshot_Halloween-Event.png", "id": "835559668776369", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974735_835559675443035_7901293442671694963_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WppWze4ArN8Q7kNvgHu3n1G&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDVpHbLEj55kykRK3_-01QowligeZpjFEWRJBWI0JuKow&oe=672A0BB4"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_1.png", "id": "1122734209200539", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974662_1122734212533872_9069853147472886357_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8-hgVN9334gQ7kNvgHzhXL4&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD46H2a1FHndhgg1YarFNYPNyXwONmPPwy39EJpGT6EUQ&oe=672A06BB"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_8.png", "id": "915022490499070", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031584_915022493832403_7622809021127260121_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QhfQkiSAh-AQ7kNvgG4PApu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCpBxORrDJzED3cdA_IM6GJ1M6uh8SkhTqdu-zRvjGkkQ&oe=672A1D31"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_3.png", "id": "1583606985872448", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75534974_1583606989205781_3814607245228628624_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AY1Lmbbx9SsQ7kNvgErl5_I&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDAwOE54yFZ9ohZecANW9FH4fqetf2H6DP4iONN_YS6Rw&oe=672A1E73"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_5.png", "id": "568201805668535", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982695_568201809001868_2618536476328559577_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xHoQt31LA7kQ7kNvgHbxAHr&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBzH-W0b3qFixEgdrarQrPjW2aduUy89bj532Yk9BNzAg&oe=672A01BB"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover_image_2560X1440.png", "id": "438961725911521", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036695_438961729244854_6523682314913022453_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=x6md-FpIwqYQ7kNvgHz3oan&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBpSPGpo1KmsPhgjY3havpsoAyVz2-5jkg3r4wCY6mfbg&oe=672A0029"}, "display_name": "Another Door: Escape Room", "keywords": ["EscapeRoom", "Puzzle", "Horror", "Coop", "Halloween"], "long_description": "# Use Your Wits To Escape!\n\nAnother Door is a VR escape room experience that plunges you into a series of immersive, unsettling environments, each with its own unique story and chilling challenges. From a trap-filled lair built by a mad scientist, to a h4unted doll's room cursed by the spirit of a dead child, and a secret laboratory where hallucinations blur reality, every episode delivers a fresh and thrilling mystery!\n{3924225681161547}\n# Another Door recreates the thrill of a physical escape room with true immersion of virtual reality.\n{1181167996493086}\n# Key Features:\n - Find hidden collectibles scattered\n - Experience five unique themes with their own puzzles\n - Escape before it\u2019s too late\n - Immersive audio de5ign\n - Online co-op\n\n# More Than Meets the Eye\nAnother Door offers f1ve distinct episodes, each with a new theme, story, and puzzle mechanics. Players can select episodes as if choosing books from a library, ensuring that no two adventures feel the same.\n{1488232228733301}\n# Play Solo or With Friends!\nPlay solo for a truly spine-tingling experience, or team up with up to three other friends to tackle the most difficult challenges together. Use voice chat to share clues and collaborate in real time as you explore and escape.\n\n# The Ultimate Test\nWhether facing the unknown alone or with friends, Another Door delivers an unforgettable VR adventure filled with suspense, teamwork, and intricate puzzles that will push your mind to its 7imits.", "short_description": "The goal is simple : Open the Door and Escape. \nStep into Another Door, an Escape Room game that challenges your logic and tests your wits. From the moment you enter, you'll face a series of devious puzzles, perfect for solo or collaborative play with friends. Built from the ground up for immersive VR, this episodic adventure brings the thrill of real-world escape rooms to virtual reality. Dive into unpredictable scenarios, decipher clues, and experience the excitement of Another Door!"}]}, "developer_name": "SKONEC Entertainment, YOUCANSTAR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": 