zBQvc0sJbZS-_1BROkNfZxPQ&oe=672A012D"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_6_2.png", "id": "441884595332750", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003249_441884598666083_391108368370507183_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=b4rDmcGFBPAQ7kNvgGc0fP0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC3Yag7HWOaB-17DVMuSq1l3X-LiKW613jtxDOAY5-T9g&oe=672A1AE6"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "2514864632034567", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982447_2514864635367900_1252665258222349809_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5JC7HeoVurcQ7kNvgG88XIh&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKaNVvQPn5eoY_JZUoPaPzmQXm5qSMDp2O-ktpsXpPCQ&oe=672A00B6"}, "display_name": "Another Door: Escape Room", "keywords": ["Puzzle", "Adventure", "Escape", "horror", "free"], "long_description": "The goal is simple : Open the Door and Escape. \n\nEverything in the room holds a hint. Embrace the challenge and immerse yourself in a world where every detail could be the key to your freedom. Another Door combines the thrill of physical escape rooms with the immersive power of VR, providing an unparalleled experience that will put your mettle to the test.\n\nHow can I enjoy the game more?\nPlaying solo is fun, but if you find the game too challenging or scary, invite a friend! Team up with others, share ideas, and solve difficult puzzles together using voice chat. You can collaborate with up to 4 players to find and decipher hints.\nI want to play with a friend!\nReconnect with a friend you haven't played with in a while. If you're feeling awkward, try the \"Buy for a friend\" option.\nAfter setting up the room, share the [room code] with your friend who bought the game. They can join easily by entering the room code. Once everyone is ready, hit [start] and enjoy escaping the room together!", "short_description": "The goal is simple : Open the Door and Escape. \nStep into Another Door, an Escape Room game that challenges your logic and tests your wits. From the moment you enter, you'll face a series of devious puzzles, perfect for solo or collaborative play with friends. Built from the ground up for immersive VR, this episodic adventure brings the thrill of real-world escape rooms to virtual reality. Dive into unpredictable scenarios, decipher clues, and experience the excitement of Another Door!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "481761404553379", "locale": "ko_KR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Another Door: Escape Room", "keywords": [], "long_description": "The goal is simple : Open the Door and Escape. \n\nEverything in the room holds a hint. Embrace the challenge and immerse yourself in a world where every detail could be the key to your freedom. Another Door combines the thrill of physical escape rooms with the immersive power of VR, providing an unparalleled experience that will put your mettle to the test.\n\nHow can I enjoy the game more?\nPlaying solo is fun, but if you find the game too challenging or scary, invite a friend! Team up with others, share ideas, and solve difficult puzzles together using voice chat. You can collaborate with up to 4 players to find and decipher hints.\nI want to play with a friend!\nReconnect with a friend you haven't played with in a while. If you're feeling awkward, try the \"Buy for a friend\" option.\nAfter setting up the room, share the [room code] with your friend who bought the game. They can join easily by entering the room code. Once everyone is ready, hit [start] and enjoy escaping the room together!", "short_description": "The goal is simple : Open the Door and Escape. \nStep into Another Door, an Escape Room game that challenges your logic and tests your wits. From the moment you enter, you'll face a series of devious puzzles, perfect for solo or collaborative play with friends. Built from the ground up f